**Key patterns:**
- All providers use `workspace:*` for internal SDK dependencies
- Dependencies: **@ai-sdk/provider** + **@ai-sdk/provider-utils** (always)
- Version: Start new packages at `0.0.0`, will be set via changeset
- Scripts: Same across all providers (build, test:node, test:edge, test, type-check)
- DevDeps: Always include @vercel/ai-tsconfig, tsup, zod

